<%- include('partials/header', { title: 'TOP', css: 'home.css', isLoggedIn }) %>
<%- include('partials/nav', { isLoggedIn }) %>
<main class="home-page home-architect-page">
    <div class="container site-container">
        <section class="home-architect-shell">
            <div class="home-architect-hero">
                <div class="home-architect-eyebrow">
                    <span>FULLSTATS</span>
                    <span>TEAM CONTROL PANEL</span>
                </div>

                <div class="home-architect-copy">
                    <p class="home-architect-lead">Overview</p>
                    <h1 class="home-architect-title">
                        チーム運用を、
                        <br>
                        静かに整理する。
                    </h1>
                    <p class="home-architect-text">
                        参加可能時間、ロール整理、進行中のタスクをひとつの画面で確認するための
                        シンプルな管理トップです。
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="home-architect-actions">
                    <% if (isLoggedIn) { %>
                        <a href="/tasks" class="btn home-architect-primary">Workspace</a>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <a href="/login" class="btn home-architect-primary">Login</a>
                    <% } %>
                    <span class="home-architect-status"><%= isLoggedIn ? 'Connected' : 'Locked' %></span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <section class="home-architect-grid">
                <article class="home-architect-panel home-architect-panel-large">
                    <div class="home-architect-panel-head">
                        <span>01</span>
                        <strong>Current Overview</strong>
                    </div>
                    <div class="home-architect-metrics">
                        <div class="home-architect-metric">
                            <span>Members</span>
                            <strong>05</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div class="home-architect-metric">
                            <span>Open Tasks</span>
                            <strong>12</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div class="home-architect-metric">
                            <span>Next Match</span>
                            <strong>19:30</strong>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="home-architect-panel">
                    <div class="home-architect-panel-head">
                        <span>02</span>
                        <strong>Availability</strong>
                    </div>
                    <p>当日の参加可能時間と開始候補を整理します。</p>
                </article>

                <article class="home-architect-panel">
                    <div class="home-architect-panel-head">
                        <span>03</span>
                        <strong>Roles</strong>
                    </div>
                    <p>担当の重複や不足を確認し、配置を整えます。</p>
                </article>

                <article class="home-architect-panel">
                    <div class="home-architect-panel-head">
                        <span>04</span>
                        <strong>Tasks</strong>
                    </div>
                    <p>次に進めるべき項目と優先度だけを一覧で確認します。</p>
                </article>

                <article class="home-architect-panel">
                    <div class="home-architect-panel-head">
                        <span>05</span>
                        <strong>Notes</strong>
                    </div>
                    <p>試合前メモや更新履歴を残し、判断の流れを共有します。</p>
                </article>
            </section>
        </section>
    </div>
</main>
<%- include('partials/footer', { isLoggedIn }) %>
